          </mj-column>
        </mj-section>

        <mj-section>
          <mj-group>
            <mj-column width="50%">
              <mj-text mj-class="header-issue">Issue No. 5</mj-text>
            </mj-column>
            <mj-column width="50%">
              <mj-text mj-class="header-date">14 Julio 2023</mj-text>
            </mj-column>
          </mj-group>
        </mj-section>

        <mj-section>
          <mj-column>
            <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="dotted" border-color="lightgrey" />
          </mj-column>
        </mj-section>
      </mj-wrapper>
      <!-- /Header -->

      <!-- Summary -->
      <mj-section mj-class="summary">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text>
            La newsletter que salen los viernes, que por fin hoy sale cuando toca.
<br><br>
En esta ocasión, es casi un especial sobre lambdas.

          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>

