						</mj-column>
					</mj-section>
				  
        
          
					<mj-section mj-class="article">
						<mj-column>
							
              <mj-text mj-class="article-title"><a href="https://medium.com/@mkristofik/modern-c-in-depth-lambdas-part-1-ad6bcebc6022">Modern C++ In-Depth — Lambdas, Part 1 | by Michael Kristofik | Medium</a></mj-text>
              
							<mj-text mj-class="article-summary">Lambdas en C++. Cuidado que hay dos partes mas!</mj-text>
						</mj-column>
					</mj-section>
				  
        
          
					<mj-section mj-class="article">
						<mj-column>
							
              <mj-text mj-class="article-title"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=42aOhzhmIpU">Lambdas, how to capture everything and stay sane - Dawid Zalewski - Meeting C++ 2022 - YouTube [video] </a></mj-text>
              
							<mj-text mj-class="article-summary">Y para no variar, un video de lambdas!</mj-text>
						</mj-column>
					</mj-section>
				  
        

        
      </mj-wrapper>

